And, to end on a lighter note, let’s talk
about what makes you happy.

00:02:15.180 --> 00:02:18.640
Let us know the one surefire way you brighten
your day in the comments.

00:02:18.640 --> 00:02:21.740
Like for me it makes me happy when people
subscribe…

